OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779930189
OL,3,CMonzo launches phone plan that gets
OL,4,Ccheaper each year
OL,6,FDigital bank Monzo is muscling into
OL,7,Fthe mobile market by launching a phone
OL,8,Fplan that gets cheaper the longer a
OL,9,Fcustomer stays.
OL,11,FCustomers of the bank can join a
OL,12,Fwaiting list for the mobile service
OL,13,Fthat is built on the Virgin O2 network
OL,14,Fand will be rolled out in the summer.
OL,16,FMonzo's entry to the market is set to
OL,17,Fintensify competition among phone
OL,18,Fproviders which are already being
OL,19,Fchallenged by newer players such as
OL,20,FRevolut and Klarna.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
