FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779930189
OL,3,CMonzo launches phone plan that gets
OL,4,Ccheaper each year
OL,6,FThe bank, which has more than 15
OL,7,Fmillion customers, said its phone plan
OL,8,Fchallenges the traditional mobile
OL,9,Fmodel by rewarding, rather than
OL,10,Fpenalising, long-term loyalty.
OL,12,FCustomers can get 5% off their monthly
OL,13,Fbill each year, resulting in a
OL,14,Fdiscount of up to 30% over time.
OL,16,FIt is offering three plans using a
OL,17,Fdigital sim and with varying data
OL,18,Fallowances, costing #8, #12, and #20 a
OL,19,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
