FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779930189
OL,3,CMonzo launches phone plan that gets
OL,4,Ccheaper each year
OL,6,FSince 2025, new rules have cracked
OL,7,Fdown on phone and broadband providers
OL,8,Fincreasing prices in the middle of a
OL,9,Fcontract without warning.
OL,11,FBut some firms have continued to come
OL,12,Funder fire for effectively penalising
OL,13,Floyal customers with inflation-linked
OL,14,Fmid-contract price rises, with
OL,15,FChancellor Rachel Reeves writing to
OL,16,Fbosses last year to demand more
OL,17,Fprotection for consumers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
