FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779930189
OL,3,CMonzo launches phone plan that gets
OL,4,Ccheaper each year
OL,6,FLike other new providers, Monzo aims
OL,7,Fto circumnavigate the issue of mid-
OL,8,Fcontract price rises by designing
OL,9,Fplans that do not tie people in for a
OL,10,Fyear and do not charge an exit fee `
OL,11,Fbut that does not mean it cannot raise
OL,12,Fthe prices of its plans at any time.
OL,14,FIn the UK, only four providers operate
OL,15,Ftheir own network infrastructure ` EE,
OL,16,FVirgin Media O2, and Vodafone and
OL,17,FThree.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
