FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779930189
OL,3,CMonzo launches phone plan that gets
OL,4,Ccheaper each year
OL,6,FBut numerous smaller providers, known
OL,7,Fas virtual networks, piggyback off
OL,8,Ftheir signals ` with Monzo using the
OL,9,FVirgin Media O2 network for its
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,FFinancial firm Revolut began rolling
OL,13,Fout a phone plan earlier this year
OL,14,Fwhich runs on the Vodafone network,
OL,15,Fand offers unlimited 5G, calls and
OL,16,Ftexts in the UK for #12.50 a month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
